name: ARMANI MANIA POUR FEMME
description: Like a stolen moment, the knowing smile of a free, authentic and affirmed nature. Far from a frozen icon, it is the very image of the Armani woman, timeless yet modern, naturally sensual and refined, checked and relaxed.
ingredients: ['Sandalwood', 'Blackcurrant', 'Magnolia', 'Cedarwood', 'Woody Notes', 'Amber', 'Iris / Orris', 'Lily Of The Valley', 'Musk', 'Peony', 'Pink Pepper', 'Laurel', 'Mandarin (green)']
